{"tid":450380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援佔中判囚　 維權女出獄　心肝膽衰弱","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T07:03:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58333e25b21560923f0ed7029516d52cbdec92bd","tid":450380,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:32:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171028/20196952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20196952&d=ttNQWDG3zbjj93Fe4ww0CdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=0ece43a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20196952&h=af9d779d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171028/20196952</a><br />\n<br />\n聲援佔中判囚　<br />\n維權女出獄　心肝膽衰弱<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171028/large/a0602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171028%2Flarge%2Fa0602a.gif&h=b78a2d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇昌蘭早前因轉發聲援佔中照片被判囚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】因聲援本港佔領運動被囚3年的廣東維權人士蘇昌蘭前日獲釋，但被指缺乏醫療照顧，健康惡化。人權組織指，蘇服刑期間健康情況急劇惡化，心臟衰弱、肝臟及膽囊均有毛病。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台報道，蘇昌蘭前日上午離開南海區看守所，其哥哥蘇尚偉當日發帖，指妹妹心情良好，但不便和外界聯絡。電台記者致電蘇尚偉，他表示不方便說話，稱妹妹獲釋後想靜心休養一段時間，暫不方便與各位朋友聯繫，待方便的時候再與大家相會，同時感謝外界一直以來的關心。<br />\n<br />\n囚室擠迫　患重病欠治療<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織發表聲明批評，南海區看守所獄中情況可怕，指監獄衞生環境差、空間窄，廁所不足，50至70人逼在80平方米的囚室，每人睡覺空間僅得50厘米闊。組織批評，蘇昌蘭服刑期間健康急劇惡化，出現心臟衰弱，肝臟及膽囊亦有毛病，指獄方未有提供足夠的醫療照顧。據報，蘇在獄中患上嚴重心臟病，律師多次申請保外就醫均被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦又批評，蘇為人權發聲但被判囚3年，絕不合理。<br />\n現年47歲的蘇昌蘭2014年10月27日因轉發香港佔領運動照片而被佛山南海區警方從家中帶走，當局以涉嫌「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」將她拘留；今年3月31日，佛山市中級法院判處蘇有期徒刑3年，她隨後提出上訴，被法院駁回，維持原判。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧燕儀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t欲申請新瑞典護照　居寧波遭軟禁　桂民海夫婦望返德國<br />\n要聞 4小時前"},{"pid":"473938d01571d126fa49a35ca74e791bc9a1b033","tid":450380,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣搞先搞到咁"},{"pid":"ff70804bbc69401f236240d1fe9609dc56e43020","tid":450380,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"玩到你就死咪放返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6e151b2d256dc4e120ec06a6328f13bcbee3b9","tid":450380,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"抵能死<br />\n<br />\n大陸狗"},{"pid":"264b52fcc5d7d9237c77ac2960429a9591ea5390","tid":450380,"uid":35094,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 樓上食屎"},{"pid":"843ae005d3118a47349e8a25fb592820ac958b88","tid":450380,"uid":9286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩到你就死咪放返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再唔係就整到你生cancer 到末期先放出黎"},{"pid":"08a82e80b849aa8f3c1b9401654aea33fa17d575","tid":450380,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"來生不做支那人"}]}